@startuml
title User Sign Up Process - RecallAI

actor User as U
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend API (.NET)" as API
participant "Postgres DB" as DB
participant "Email Service" as EM

' Sign up
activate U
U -> FE : Enters Username and Password
activate FE
FE -> API : POST /register (username, password)
activate API
API -> DB : Creates entry for user
activate DB
API -> EM : OTP Email Request
activate EM
EM -> U : Sends OTP via Email
deactivate EM
U -> FE : Enters OTP
FE -> API : POST /verify-otp (otp)
API -> DB : Marks user as verified

' Login
U -> FE : Enters Username and Password
FE -> API : POST /login (username, password)
API -> DB : Checks credentials
DB -> API : Credentials matched / mismatched
deactivate DB
API -> FE : Login Success / Failure
deactivate API
deactivate FE

@enduml
